snippet.title: Gta 5 Dinka Thrust Location | Story Mode | Can Only be Stolen (PS5/4/3, Xbox One/X/360, PC) 2022
snippet.description:
🔹️Skip the first half of the video if you already watch one of these motorcycle location videos.

00:40 - Location

Hey what's up you guys, im back with another tutorial on Gta V. So today I'm gonna show you how to find Dinka Thrust in Gta 5 Story Mode(offline) with the spawn locations and other random locations that you can find these motorcycles. This Motorcycle is not able to purchase in the story mode and only can be stolen to aquire one.

You'll find almost everything you need to know upto date because im playing on the one of the latest version which is 2372 build, 1.57 online (1.58 is the most recent one) and i can ensure that these locations and methods are working across most of the platforms including ps5, ps4, xbox one, xbox series x and pc(which im demonstrating). If you're a returning player on ps3 and xbox 360, you'll also be able to find these motorcycles.
